Category: Q&A
  Title: Why won't my user-level hook fire in Cowork?
  Body:  User-level hooks (~/.claude/settings.json hooks block,
         ~/.claude/hooks/) do not fire in Cowork's Code tab. Known
         platform limitation — see GitHub issue anthropics/claude-code#27398.
         hardgate installs at project-level .claude/ automatically.

Category: Ideas
  Title: What should hardgate gate next?
  Body:  Share your plugin/skill/shortcut that Claude Code keeps ignoring.
         Good candidates: token-saving plugins, quality gates, TDD process
         enforcement, pre-commit checks.

Category: Show and tell
